{
  "texts": [
    "The 6G service-based RAN based on cloud-native technologies aims to decouple traditional integrated single-BS functions into control and user plane services, achieve interaction and open capabilities between functional services using service-based interfaces, and provide more flexible and streamlined network capabilities in an on-demand combination.",
    "These functionalities help improve the network's adaptability to the entire industry (Li N et al., 2022a).",
    "This RAN includes mainly the following three technical features (China Mobile, 2022):",
    "Feature 1: cloud user interface.",
    "Functional decoupling is a necessary step to develop a servicebased RAN."
  ]
}